  "text": "However, the resulting UD ionospheric delays are biased. At the step 3 (rover solution), the interpolated UD ionospheric delays were again converted to DD delays which serve as weighted corrections [CITATION_1] . Note that, UD biases are removed when DD ionospheric corrections are calculated (due to differencing of the UD corrections).",
